text: West France is a European Parliament constituency. It currently elects 10 MEPs. It includes the French regions of Brittany, Pays de la Loire, and the former region Poitou-Charentes (now part of region Nouvelle-Aquitaine). ==Results== ===2009=== ===2004=== Brackets indicate the number of votes per seat won. ==See also== * European Parliament election results for France in 2004 Category:European Parliament constituencies in France Category:2004 establishments in France Category:Constituencies established in 2004
